---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/base-layout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Kıymet Veteriner Kliniği - İzmir Bornova'da Güvenilir Veteriner Hizmetleri"
  description="Kıymet Veteriner Kliniği olarak İzmir Bornova'da 7/24 acil veteriner hizmetleri, genel muayene, aşı takibi, cerrahi işlemler sunuyoruz. Hürriyet Cd. No:238"
  keywords="veteriner İzmir, Bornova veteriner, acil veteriner, kedi köpek muayene, aşı takibi, veteriner cerrahi, Kıymet Veteriner"
>
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
      class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 via-white to-blue-50 pt-20"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40">
        <div
          class="h-full w-full bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iNjAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA2MCA2MCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj48ZyBmaWxsPSJub25lIiBmaWxsLXJ1bGU9ImV2ZW5vZGQiPjxnIGZpbGw9IiNlMGYyZmUiIGZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eT0iMC4zIj48Y2lyY2xlIGN4PSIzMCIgY3k9IjMwIiByPSIyIi8+PC9nPjwvZz48L3N2Zz4=')]"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Hero Content -->
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
            <div
              class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-sky-800"
            >
              <svg
                class="mr-2 h-4 w-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              7/24 Veteriner Hizmetleri
            </div>

            <h1
              class="mb-6 text-4xl leading-tight font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
            >
              Kıymet Veteriner Kliniği
            </h1>

            <p class="mb-8 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
              İzmir Bornova'da evcil dostlarınızın sağlığı için profesyonel
              veteriner hizmetleri. Modern ekipmanlar ve deneyimli kadromuzla,
              sevgili hayvanlarınızın sağlık ve mutluluğunu en üst düzeyde
              tutuyoruz.
            </p>

            <div
              class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row lg:justify-start"
            >
              <a
                href="/randevu"
                class="group inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-sky-600 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-sky-700 hover:shadow-xl"
              >
                <svg
                  class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                Randevu Al
              </a>
              <a
                href="tel:+905386944455"
                class="group inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-red-600 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-red-700 hover:shadow-xl"
              >
                <svg
                  class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 group-hover:animate-pulse"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                Acil Arama
              </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Stats -->
            <div
              class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 border-t border-gray-200 pt-8"
            >
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-1 text-3xl font-bold text-sky-600">15+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Yıl Deneyim</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-1 text-3xl font-bold text-sky-600">5000+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Mutlu Müşteri</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-1 text-3xl font-bold text-sky-600">24/7</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Acil Hizmet</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Hero Image -->
          <div class="relative">
            <div
              class="relative z-10 rotate-3 transform rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:rotate-0"
            >
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551717743-49959800b1f6?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
                alt="Veteriner Muayene"
                class="h-96 w-full rounded-2xl object-cover"
              />
              <div
                class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 rounded-2xl bg-sky-500 p-4 text-white shadow-lg"
              >
                <svg
                  class="h-8 w-8"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 -rotate-6 transform rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-400 to-blue-500 opacity-20"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Hizmetlerimiz</h2>
          <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-xl text-gray-600">
            Evcil hayvanlarınız için kapsamlı sağlık hizmetleri sunuyoruz
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Genel Muayene -->
          <div
            class="group rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50 p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-500 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Genel Muayene
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">
              Düzenli sağlık kontrolleri ile evcil dostlarınızın sağlığını
              koruyoruz.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/hizmetler/genel-muayene"
              class="font-semibold text-sky-600 transition-colors hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Detaylı Bilgi →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Aşı & Sağlık -->
          <div
            class="group rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-green-50 p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-green-500 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Aşı & Sağlık Takibi
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">
              Zamanında aşılama ve düzenli sağlık takibi hizmetleri.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/hizmetler/asi-saglik"
              class="font-semibold text-green-600 transition-colors hover:text-green-700"
            >
              Detaylı Bilgi →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Cerrahi -->
          <div
            class="group rounded-2xl border border-purple-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-purple-50 p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-purple-500 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Cerrahi İşlemler
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">
              Modern ameliyathane ve deneyimli cerrah kadromuz.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/hizmetler/cerrahi"
              class="font-semibold text-purple-600 transition-colors hover:text-purple-700"
            >
              Detaylı Bilgi →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Laboratuvar -->
          <div
            class="group rounded-2xl border border-orange-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-orange-50 p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-orange-500 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Laboratuvar
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">
              Hızlı ve güvenilir laboratuvar test sonuçları.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/hizmetler/laboratuvar"
              class="font-semibold text-orange-600 transition-colors hover:text-orange-700"
            >
              Detaylı Bilgi →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Acil Müdahale -->
          <div
            class="group rounded-2xl border border-red-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-red-50 p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-red-500 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Acil Müdahale
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">
              7/24 acil durum müdahale hizmetlerimiz.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/hizmetler/acil"
              class="font-semibold text-red-600 transition-colors hover:text-red-700"
            >
              Detaylı Bilgi →
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Diş Bakımı -->
          <div
            class="group rounded-2xl border border-teal-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-teal-50 p-8 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-500 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h1.01M15 10h1.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
              Diş Bakımı
            </h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600">Ağız ve diş sağlığı hizmetleri.</p>
            <a
              href="/hizmetler/dis-bakimi"
              class="font-semibold text-teal-600 transition-colors hover:text-teal-700"
            >
              Detaylı Bilgi →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Neden VetKlinik?
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-gray-600">
              15 yıllık deneyimimiz ve modern ekipmanlarımızla evcil
              dostlarınıza en iyi bakımı sağlıyoruz.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div
                  class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sky-500"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    Deneyimli Kadro
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    15+ yıl deneyimli veteriner hekimlerimiz
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div
                  class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sky-500"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    Modern Ekipman
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">En son teknoloji tıbbi cihazlar</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div
                  class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sky-500"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    7/24 Hizmet
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Acil durumlar için kesintisiz hizmet
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576201836106-db1758fd1c97?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
              alt="Veteriner Kliniği"
              class="h-96 w-full rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-2xl"
            />
            <div
              class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-xl"
            >
              <div class="mb-1 text-3xl font-bold text-sky-600">5000+</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600">Mutlu Müşteri</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section
      class="mb-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 to-blue-700 py-20 text-white"
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center lg:px-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">
          Evcil Dostunuz İçin Randevu Alın
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-xl opacity-90">
          Profesyonel veteriner hizmetlerimizden yararlanmak için hemen randevu
          oluşturun.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="/randevu"
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-white px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-sky-600 shadow-lg transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <svg
              class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Online Randevu Al
          </a>
          <a
            href="/iletisim"
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border-2 border-white px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white hover:text-sky-600"
          >
            <svg
              class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"
              ></path>
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            Bizi Ziyaret Edin
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
